'''平臺獨占'''（{{lang-en|console exclusivity}}）是指一套[[電玩遊戲|電玩遊戲]]僅限在某款[[電子遊樂器|電子遊樂器]]上推出的情況。平臺獨占會被用來討論競爭對手公司於電玩市場的優劣勢，也會被公司用來[[行銷|行銷]]。產業分析師通常會同意，在擁有多少獨占遊戲，與硬體的銷售量之間，會有所關連。大型公司為了確保軟體產品，也會購買較小的企業。平臺獨占偶爾也會出現在於多個平臺上推出的軟體，其中每個不同的版本間都有著不同的獨特元素。

== 產業內平臺獨占的運用 ==

微軟通常會在其獨占遊戲的盒子上貼上「Only on [[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]」之類的標籤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/console/xbox360/image/954261.html?box=125822|title=EU Boxshot of Halo 3: ODST|date=2009-10-22|publisher=GameFAQs|accessdate=2009-11-16|archive-date=2010-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100423035916/http://www.gamefaqs.com/console/xbox360/image/954261.html?box=125822|dead-url=no}}</ref>。許多此類獨占遊戲會被用來在 [[E3电子娱乐展|E3]] 等大會中展示，以協助提升[[電腦硬體|硬體]]的銷量，因為消費者會因各類平臺上所擁有的遊戲種類而左右其選擇。分析師曾表示，過去的銷售額已顯示，在硬體的銷售，以及專屬於其硬體的軟體推出之間，有所關連<ref name="ps3sale">{{cite web|url=http://uk.gamespot.com/ps3/adventure/metalgearsolid4/news.html?sid=6194691|title=PS3 sales spike on Metal Gear Solid 4 release|last=Magrino|first=Tom|date=2008-07-18|publisher=GameSpot|accessdate=2009-11-16|archive-date=2013-01-24|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130124151959/http://uk.gamespot.com/ps3/adventure/metalgearsolid4/news.html?sid=6194691|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。亦有資料顯示，在假期時，消費者的花費通常會較高，擁有較多獨占遊戲的硬體通常會賣得比只有較少選擇的硬體來得好<ref name="sgraph">{{cite web|url=http://www.totalvideogames.com/PlayStation-3/feature-14420.html|title=7th Generation Feature: Lifetime sales of consoles|last=Leyton|first=Chris|date=2009-07-24|publisher=totalvideogames.com|accessdate=2009-11-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727213049/http://www.totalvideogames.com/PlayStation-3/feature-14420.html|archivedate=2009-07-27}}</ref>。[[軟體|軟體]]的銷售量與相關硬體的銷售之間亦顯示關連性，如在2009年底，[[Wii|Wii]] 在硬體與軟體的銷售上均名列前位<ref name="nindo">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/6946610.stm|title=Nintendo dominates UK games chart|date=2007-08-14|publisher=news.bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2009-11-16|archive-date=2008-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129215319/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/6946610.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 平臺獨占對銷售額的影響 ==

除了銷售數據支持硬體銷售與軟體產品間的關係<ref name="ps3sale" /><ref name="sgraph" />外，[[CNET|CNET]]（擁有[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]與[[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]等公司）表示，「最大的決策在於，選擇電玩遊戲所要獨占的平臺<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-10268239-1.html|title=Xbox 360 exclusive gaming|last=Bakalar|first=Jeff|date=2009-06-18|publisher=CNET News|accessdate=2009-11-16|archive-date=2009-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090805012908/http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-10268239-1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」在 E3 上，每家業者所提出的獨占遊戲亦反映了獨占遊戲，以及獨占硬體之行銷能力<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/e3-2009/5429957/E3-2009-Is-Microsofts-Natal-system-the-future-of-gaming.html|title=E3 2009: Is Microsoft's Natel system the future of gaming?|last=Beaumont|first=Claudine|date=2009-06-02|publisher=Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2009-11-16|location=London|archive-date=2009-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090731182439/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/e3-2009/5429957/E3-2009-Is-Microsofts-Natal-system-the-future-of-gaming.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/5424736/E3-2009-Xbox-360-exclusives.html|title=E3 2009: Xbox 360 exclusives slideshow|publisher=Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2009-11-16|location=London|date=2009-06-01|archive-date=2010-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100125130601/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/5424736/E3-2009-Xbox-360-exclusives.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

許多媒體報導會將獨占[[電腦硬體|硬體]]與[[軟體|軟體]]作為[[消費者|消費者]]考慮的要點<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/8272807.stm|title=Video game console wars reignite|last=Emery|first=Daniel|date=2009-09-25|publisher=news.bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2009-11-16}}</ref>。他們還會注意開發商推出的獨占遊戲之相關性，因為當這些遊戲在多個平臺上推出時，可能會有更高的銷售額<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/8078629.stm|title=Exclusive games go multi-platform|last=Emery|first=Daniel|date=2009-06-02|publisher=news.bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2009-11-16|archive-date=2009-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090605164148/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/8078629.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[微軟|微軟]]、[[Sony|Sony]]與[[任天堂|任天堂]]等公司也會將獨占遊戲作為其[[营销战略|行銷策略]]。微軟宣稱，[[最後一戰系列|最後一戰系列]]，尤其是[[最後一戰3|最後一戰3]]，是該公司以 [[Xbox|Xbox]] 與 [[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]] 等遊戲機進入電玩市場時，採取策略中的重要「誘因」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/8078629.stm|title=Hits and misses of Microsoft|last=Ward|first=Mark|date=2008-06-27|publisher=news.bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2009-11-16|archive-date=2009-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090605164148/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/8078629.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="h3strat">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/7014292.stm|title=Halo 3 central to Microsoft's strategy|last=Joyce|first=Julian|date=2007-09-26|publisher=news.bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2009-11-16|archive-date=2007-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071221233349/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/7014292.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Sony 與微軟之類的大公司為維持獨占而買下小型的開發商，則不太常見<ref name="h3strat" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/4882330.stm|title=Microsoft snaps up UK games guru|last=Hermida|first=Alfred|date=2006-04-06|publisher=news.bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2009-11-16|archive-date=2007-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070330190059/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/4882330.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Wii 的支配地位<ref name="nindo" /><ref name="sixone">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/6265368.stm|title=Wii outsells PS3 "six to one"|date=2007-07-03|publisher=news.bbc.co.uk|accessdate=2009-11-16|archive-date=2009-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090111214207/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/6265368.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>亦吸引了媒體關注其獨占技術與銷售<ref name="h3strat" />，勝過其硬體內的純粹技術。微軟甚至為了降低任天堂在{{le|運動控制器|Motion Controller|運動控制}}技術上的支配地位，推出了 [[Kinect|Kinect]]。同樣地，分析師表示，PlayStation 缺乏「殺手級獨占遊戲」，是該平臺在2007年銷售不良的原因之一<ref name="sixone" />。

== 其他方法 ==

平臺獨占亦可能以在特定平臺上擁有獨特之功能來呈現<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.xbox360achievements.org/news/news-4066-Sonic-&-Sega-All-Stars-Racing-Adds-Banjo-Kazooie----and-You-.html|title=Sonic and Sega All-stars exclusive 360 characters|last=Pettit|first=Alan|date=2009-12-19|publisher=Xbox360Achievements.org|accessdate=2010-01-15|archive-date=2010-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100122110002/http://www.xbox360achievements.org/news/news-4066-Sonic-%26-Sega-All-Stars-Racing-Adds-Banjo-Kazooie----and-You-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。例如，[[魂之系列|魂之系列]]的每個版本在不同的平臺上都會有不同的獨創角色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.gamespot.com/gamecube/action/soulcalibur2/review.html|title=Soul Calibur II at GameSpot|last=Kasavin|first=Greg|date=2003-08-26|publisher=GameSpot|accessdate=2010-01-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071007175628/http://uk.gamespot.com/gamecube/action/soulcalibur2/review.html|archivedate=2007-10-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.gamespot.com/news/6199611.html|title=Soul Calibur IV news|author=Polybren|date=2008-10-18|publisher=GameSpot|accessdate=2010-01-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120718040128/http://uk.gamespot.com/news/6199611.html|archivedate=2012-07-18}}</ref>。

